Class AppointmentRecord

java.lang.Object
model.HMSRecords
model.AppointmentRecord
public class AppointmentRecord extends HMSRecords
Represents an appointment record, containing patient details, appointment time, status, location, and associated appointment outcome. This class extends HMSRecords.
